codeText: protected void createIndicesWithRandomAliases(String... indices) {_        createIndex(indices)___        if (frequently()) {_            IndicesAliasesRequestBuilder builder = client().admin().indices().prepareAliases()__            for (String index : indices) {_                if (frequently()) {_                    _                    builder.addAlias(index, "alias-" + index)__                }_            }_            if (randomBoolean()) {_                _                for (String index : indices) {_                    builder.addAlias(index, "alias")__                }_            }_            assertAcked(builder)__        }__        for (String index : indices) {_            client().prepareIndex(index, "type").setSource("field", "value").get()__        }_        refresh(indices)__    }
